#. js-lingui-explicit-id
#: src/components/faq/Content.tsx:21
msgid "What is Linkary?"
msgstr "Linkary 是什么？"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
#: src/components/faq/Content.tsx:22
msgid "Linkary is a web service to reliably save and manage links and, if you want, share them with the community. It checks potentially harmful links and provides AI-powered personalized recommendations."
msgstr "Linkary 是一个可靠保存和管理链接的网络服务，如果您愿意，还可以与社区分享。它检查潜在有害链接，并提供 AI 驱动的个性化推荐。"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
#: src/components/faq/Content.tsx:28
msgid "Do you offer a paid plan?"
msgstr "您提供付费计划吗？"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
#: src/components/faq/Content.tsx:29
msgid "There is no separate paid plan, and each user's usage quota resets at 00:00 on the 1st of every month."
msgstr "没有单独的付费计划，每个用户的使用配额在每月1日00:00重置。"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
#: src/components/faq/Content.tsx:35
msgid "Are links marked \"safe\" guaranteed to be safe?"
msgstr "标记为\"安全\"的链接保证安全吗？"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
#: src/components/faq/Content.tsx:36
msgid "We assess risk via the Google Web Risk API, but undetected threats or errors may occur, so absolute safety cannot be guaranteed. Details: https://cloud.google.com/web-risk/docs/overview"
msgstr "我们通过 Google Web Risk API 评估风险，但可能会出现未检测到的威胁或错误，因此无法保证绝对安全。详情：<a>https://cloud.google.com/web-risk/docs/overview</a>"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
#: src/components/faq/Content.tsx:42
msgid "Can I save links without sharing them?"
msgstr "我可以保存链接而不分享它们吗？"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
#: src/components/faq/Content.tsx:43
msgid "Yes. Sharing is optional, and the default is private (not shared)."
msgstr "可以。分享是可选的，默认为私有（不分享）。"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
#: src/components/faq/Content.tsx:49
msgid "How is my personal data used?"
msgstr "我的个人数据如何使用？"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
#: src/components/faq/Content.tsx:50
msgid "We collect only minimal data (Google OAuth identifier and email) for sign-up and use it solely for login/account management. Upon deletion, data is erased without undue delay, except where retention is required by law."
msgstr "我们只收集注册所需的最少数据（Google OAuth 标识符和电子邮件），仅用于登录/账户管理。删除时，除法律要求保留的情况外，数据会被及时清除。"

